:QUOTE
Your voice at its best, every episode, without a recording booth.

:INFO
AI Voiceover for Solo Podcasters
AI voice tools let solo podcasters produce clean, professional-sounding audio without expensive equipment or repeated takes. ElevenLabs and similar tools generate realistic speech from your script.

:COUNTER.half
10 Minutes
Average generation time for a 20 min episode
|
:COUNTER.half
95% Accuracy
Quality match to professional voiceover at top settings

:PATH
Script Phase
Write a clean, conversational script. Avoid symbols and abbreviations. Mark pauses with punctuation and line breaks.

:PATH
Generate Phase
Paste your script into ElevenLabs or your chosen tool. Select or clone your voice. Adjust stability and clarity settings.

:PATH
Edit Phase
Import generated audio into Descript or Audacity. Clean silence gaps, add music bed, export as MP3.

:CHECKLIST
Voiceover Workflow Checklist
[ ] Write and proofread full script
[ ] Format script for natural speech flow
[ ] Generate audio with voice tool
[ ] Listen through at 1x speed for errors
[ ] Edit in audio editor
[ ] Add intro and outro music
[ ] Export and upload to podcast host

:NOTE
ElevenLabs voice cloning works best when trained on clean audio with no background noise or music. Record a 10-minute sample in a quiet room with a decent USB microphone.

